# 8. 揺るぎなく、ここに

Kotaro: Man, the battle's over, but everyone's still bouncing off the walls...
Tatsuya: Yeah.
Tatsuya: ...
Toya: Okazaki?
Tatsuya: She won... Against herself.
Tatsuya: That day when we battled against Taiga... I became convinced that there was no way for us to win.
Tatsuya: It felt like I was on my motorcycle smashing head-first into a semi.
Tatsuya: But... I'm not sure I should've given up so easily.
Tatsuya: We originally began singing because we really admired this one senior of ours who was chasing after an impossible dream that others laughed at.
Tatsuya: But we decided to stop chasing the impossible... We said, “We'll never succeed, so why bother?”
Tatsuya: But that was clearly just an excuse.
Tatsuya: The prospect of not winning, of losing that badly again... We haven't been able to shake that fear.
Tatsuya: It started to feel like a fact we couldn't change.
Tatsuya: But Shiraishi...won that fight.
Tatsuya: She overcame the fear within herself.
EVER Member: ...
Toya: She did.
Tatsuya: She's really something else.
Tatsuya: So, you guys, how about we quit running already...?
EVER Member: ...!
Tatsuya: We need to keep fighting until we find a way to win.
Tatsuya: That's our mission. That's why we're called EVER.
Toya: Okazaki...
EVER Member: Yeah, you're right...
EVER Member: We gotta get back on track...
Tatsuya: We're really sorry.
Tatsuya: Will you let us back into your group?
An: *Nod* Looks like things are starting to settle down.
An: Listen up, everyone!
An: We're going to go beyond Nagi's dream!
Owner of Crawl Green: ...!
Local Musicians: Nagi? Who's that...?
Local Musicians: Wait, you don't know? She was a member of RADder.
Local Musicians: So, that means going beyond RADder... Like, surpassing RAD WEEKEND?
An: I want to take her hopes and dreams and go where she couldn't.
An: I want to take what she entrusted me with that night and make her proud.
Attractive Lady: An...
An: And...
An: I want you all to join us.
Owner of Crawl Green: ...
An: No, you're coming with us whether you like it or not!!
An: Nagi's dream! All of your hopes!
An: We're gonna carry them with us! We're gonna take them to heights you can't imagine!
An: We're gonna show all of you something that you couldn't see even at RAD WEEKEND!
An: So...
An: Come with us!!!
Frizzly-Haired Record Store Clerk: ...
Attractive Lady: An...
Owner of Crawl Green: An!!
Owner of Crawl Green: We'll be there to watch.
Owner of Crawl Green: To see where you all go.
An: Good!
An: Thanks, everyone!
Kohane: Hehe.
Kohane: You're so cool.
An: Thanks for doing this with me today, Kohane.
An: I was able to overcome all the doubt and fear I've been feeling up until now.
Kohane: No, I should be the one thanking you.
Kohane: What we did today made me want to get even better.
An: ... Do you think you'll be able to accomplish your task, Kohane?
Kohane: *Nod*
Kohane: It's going to be really hard... But I think I will be able to now.
An: Okay.
An: In that case, I'll be looking forward to seeing some good results, partner.
Toya: Shiraishi!!
An: Hey, you guys...! Thanks for coming to watch us!
Akito: We should be the ones thanking you. They decided to come back because of what you just did.
An: Huh? Oh, EVER's here...!
Tatsuya: Your battle helped open our eyes.
Tatsuya: We look forward to working with you all again.
An: Likewise! Thanks so much for deciding to come back!
An: Anyway, let's go, you guys!
An: Next time, we're for sure gonna surpass RAD WEEKEND!
